        </h1>

        <p>
        "In the 2017 State of DevOps report, Puppet found that high-performing
        DevOps teams had:
        </p>
        <ul class="nested">
            <li>
                46 times more frequent code deployments
            </li>
            <li>
                440 times faster lead time from commit to deploy
            </li>
            <li>
                96 times faster mean time to recover from downtime
            </li>
            <li>
                5 times lower change failure rate (changes are 1/5 as likely to
                fail)"
            </li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            (Source: <a
                                                href="https://stackify.com/top-devops-blogs/">Stackify</a>.)
